- um am Ende gar in den Standard ,aufsteigen‘ zu können.  aThis “corpus-driven” work contributes to the investigation of grammatical phenomena in the linguistic period of New High German (17th to 21st centuries) with a focus on pronominal adverbs (e.g. davon weiß ich nichts; da weiß ich nichts von; da weiß ich nichts davon; dadavon weiß ich nichts). This analysis follows the trend of current grammar research by concentrating on registers of spoken German.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aGerman languagexAdverb. 0aGerman languagexGrammarxHistory. 0aGerman languagexPronominalsxHistory. 0aGerman languagexPronominals. 0aGerman languagexSocial aspectsxHistory. 4aSprachsoziologie. 4aSyntax. 4aUmgangssprache. 4aVariation (Sprache). 7aFOREIGN LANGUAGE STUDY / German.2bisacsh  aVariation (linguistics).  acolloquial language.  alinguistic sociology.  asyntax.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2012z9783110288896oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978311027311340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311027328140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110273281423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110273281/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGAb2012  aZDB-23-DGGb2012  aZDB-23-DLSc2000d2014